verbose_text: Most of the BA group who had positive VEGF expression in BDs (89.3%) and AWs (92.6%) in liver tissues also showed positive subcapsular hepatic flow, while most of the non BA group who had negative VEGF expression in BDs (94.1%) and AWs (93.9%) in liver tissues showed negative subcapsular hepatic flow by color Doppler (p < 0.05).
